e rich than they are at the present epoch,\nwhich is consistent with observations. These quantitative results, derived\nsolely from observations, agree well with cosmological simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2009 20:03:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 May 2010 18:14:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 10 May 2010 22:15:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
