ing backward): This\nphenomenon will be called Moonwalking. Most of our results are illustrated by\nnumerical examples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2009 21:27:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2009 17:30:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Oct 2009 19:15:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-29"}
